            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Here's an admission: I always viewed the author of this piece - Marie Le Conte - as one of the performative attention farmers on Twitter, who had significantly aided her career by being actively controversial on there. She doesn't really disabuse me of that notion in this piece, and I ",
